title: Choi Moo-lim
text: Choi Moo-Lim (; born 15 April 1979) is a former <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Goalkeeper%20%28association%20football%29">goalkeeper</a> from <a href="South%20Korea">South Korea</a>. He formerly played for <a href="Ulsan%20Hyundai%20FC">Ulsan Hyundai</a> in the <a href="K-League">K-League</a> for 10 seasons.
